{"title":"女娲之歌","authors":["魏明伦"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"女娲之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婴儿一声啼——妈妈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子千声唤——妈妈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西方的妈妈——夏娃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方的妈妈——女娲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺两座白玉高峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披双肩乌云长发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮一身健美曲线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插几朵怒放野花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由、潇洒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤条条来往无牵挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采山川灵秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸日月精华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒爱的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播情的根芽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒遍华夏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播向天涯……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲人间重重灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忧众神纷纷残杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灭大地熊熊战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"补苍天累累伤疤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造、开发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇灌和平玫瑰花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"导九曲黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织五彩云霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是女娲后代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是当代女娲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤人性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振兴中华。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}